+.BI -w
+to wait for entries to be logged
+
+.TP
+.BI -f
+file to log to specified file
+
+.TP
+.BI -x
+read ISDN trace
+
+.TP
+.BI -c
+read CAPI trace
+
+.TP
+.BI -i
+read IDI trace
