+.SH NAME
+divalogd \- utility to record messages from Diva cards
+.SH SYNOPSIS
+divalogd [ num ]
+.SH DESCRIPTION
+.B divalogd
+connects to a logging device (/dev/Divas)
+to receive messages form Diva cards, which
